column2: SELECT  	po.objid AS phot_id, po.ra AS phot_ra, po.dec AS phot_dec,  	ISNULL(pz.z, #) AS phot_z, ISNULL(pz.zerr, #) AS phot_zerr,  	po.type AS phot_type, po.ndetect AS phot_ndet, po.clean AS phot_clean,  	ISNULL(sp.specobjid, #) AS spec_id, ISNULL(sp.ra, #) AS spec_ra, ISNULL(sp.dec, #) AS spec_dec, 	ISNULL(sp.z, #) AS spec_z, ISNULL(sp.zerr, #) AS spec_zerr,  	ISNULL(sp.class, #) AS spec_class, ISNULL(sp.instrument, #) AS spec_inst,  	po.cmodelmag_u AS cmodmag_u, po.cmodelmagerr_u AS cmoderr_u, po.fibermag_u AS fib3mag_u, po.fiber2mag_u AS fib2mag_u, po.extinction_u AS extinct_u,  	po.cmodelmag_g AS cmodmag_g, po.cmodelmagerr_g AS cmoderr_g, po.fibermag_g AS fib3mag_g, po.fiber2mag_g AS fib2mag_g, po.extinction_g AS extinct_g,  	po.cmodelmag_r AS cmodmag_r, po.cmodelmagerr_r AS cmoderr_r, po.fibermag_r AS fib3mag_r, po.fiber2mag_r AS fib2mag_r, po.extinction_r AS extinct_r,  	po.cmodelmag_i AS cmodmag_i, po.cmodelmagerr_i AS cmoderr_i, po.fibermag_i AS fib3mag_i, po.fiber2mag_i AS fib2mag_i, po.extinction_i AS extinct_i,  	po.cmodelmag_z AS cmodmag_z, po.cmodelmagerr_z AS cmoderr_z, po.fibermag_z AS fib3mag_z, po.fiber2mag_z AS fib2mag_z, po.extinction_z AS extinct_z, 	wx.wise_cntr AS wise_id, wa.ra AS wise_ra, wa.dec AS wise_dec, wx.match_dist AS wise_dist, wa.blend_ext_flags AS wise_flag, 	wa.w1mpro AS wise_promag_w1, wa.w1sigmpro AS wise_prosig_w1, wa.w1snr AS wise_prosnr_w1, wa.w1m AS wise_pronum_w1, wa.w1mag_# AS wise_apemag_w1, wa.w1sigm_# AS wise_apesig_w1,  	wa.w2mpro AS wise_promag_w2, wa.w2sigmpro AS wise_prosig_w2, wa.w2snr AS wise_prosnr_w2, wa.w2m AS wise_pronum_w2, wa.w2mag_# AS wise_apemag_w2, wa.w2sigm_# AS wise_apesig_w2,  	wa.w3mpro AS wise_promag_w3, wa.w3sigmpro AS wise_prosig_w3, wa.w3snr AS wise_prosnr_w3, wa.w3m AS wise_pronum_w3, wa.w3mag_# AS wise_apemag_w3, wa.w3sigm_# AS wise_apesig_w3,  	wa.w4mpro AS wise_promag_w4, wa.w4sigmpro AS wise_prosig_w4, wa.w4snr AS wise_prosnr_w4, wa.w4m AS wise_pronum_w4, wa.w4mag_# AS wise_apemag_w4, wa.w4sigm_# AS wise_apesig_w4,  	ISNULL(tm.j_m_k2#fe, #) AS tmass_mag_j, ISNULL(tm.j_msig_k2#fe, #) AS tmass_sig_j, 	ISNULL(tm.h_m_k2#fe, #) AS tmass_mag_h, ISNULL(tm.h_msig_k2#fe, #) AS tmass_sig_h, 	ISNULL(tm.k_m_k2#fe, #) AS tmass_mag_k, ISNULL(tm.k_msig_k2#fe, #) AS tmass_sig_k, 	ISNULL(ft.peak, #) AS first_peak, ISNULL(ft.rms, #) AS first_rms   INTO MyDB.SDSSspecDR1#_WISExmatch FROM PhotoPrimary po  	LEFT OUTER JOIN Photoz      pz ON pz.objid      = po.objid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN SpecObj     sp ON sp.bestobjid  = po.objid 	     INNER JOIN WISE_xmatch wx ON wx.sdss_objid = po.objid 	     INNER JOIN WISE_allsky wa ON wa.cntr       = wx.wise_cntr 	LEFT OUTER JOIN TwoMassXSC  tm ON tm.objid      = po.objid 	LEFT OUTER JOIN FIRST       ft ON ft.objid      = po.objid      WHERE   	((po.flags & #) != #)         	AND ((po.flags & #) = #)  	                                       	                                       	                                       	                                       	                                       	                                       	AND (((po.flags & #) = #) OR (po.psfmagerr_g <= #)) 	         	         	AND (((po.flags & #) = #) OR (po.flags & #) = #) 	         	         	AND (po.calibStatus_g & #) != # 	AND (po.calibStatus_r & #) != # 	AND (po.calibStatus_i & #) != # 	AND po.cmodelmagerr_g <= #  	AND po.cmodelmagerr_r <= #  	AND po.cmodelmagerr_i <= #  	AND ( wa.w1cc_map = # AND wa.w2cc_map = # AND wa.w3cc_map = # AND wa.w4cc_map = # ) 	AND ( wa.w1m     >= # AND wa.w2m     >= # AND wa.w3m     >= # AND wa.w4m     >= # ) 	AND ( wa.w1snr   >= # AND wa.w2snr   >= # AND wa.w3snr   >= # AND wa.w4snr   >= # )                ORDER BY phot_id
